<view wx:if="{{show==false}}">
<van-col span="22" offset="1" custom-class="ID">合作申请</van-col>
<van-col span="22" offset="1" custom-class="ID-desc">您需要选择以下任意条件可领取推荐奖励</van-col>
<van-col span="22" offset="1" custom-class="card" wx:for="{{list}}" wx:key="key" wx:for-index="key">
  <van-col span="22"offset="1"custom-class="card-top">
    <text class="card-top-desc">{{item.name}}</text>
    <text class="card-top-bt" wx:if="{{item.status==2||item.status==3}}" data-index="{{key}}" data-type="{{item.type}}" bindtap="addPartner">申请</text>
    <text class="on" wx:if="{{item.status!=2&&item.status!=3}}">申请</text>
  </van-col>
  <van-col span="22"offset="1"custom-class="desc">这里是社会合伙人简单说明。</van-col>
  <van-col span="22"offset="1"custom-class="card-bottom" wx:if="{{item.status==3}}">提交申请，待后台验证</van-col>
  <van-col span="22"offset="1"custom-class="card-bottoms" wx:if="{{item.status==0}}">审核中</van-col>
  <van-col span="22"offset="1"custom-class="card-bottomss" wx:if="{{item.status==1}}">审核已通过</van-col>
  <van-col span="22"offset="1"custom-class="card-bottomsss" wx:if="{{item.status==2}}">未通过<text style="font-size: 20rpx;color:#666666">（可联系客服咨询详情，重新申请）</text></van-col>
</van-col>
